{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-functions-in-javascript/lab-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter/build-a-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter","demoType":null,"title":"Prevedi temperaturu iz Celzijusa u Farenhajta","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovoj laboratoriji, treba da napišete funkciju koja konvertuje temperaturu iz Celisiusa u Farenhajta. Formula za konverziju iz Celisiusa u Farenhajta je:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">fahrenheit = celsius * (9/5) + 32\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Cilj:</strong> Popunite korisničke priče ispod i prođite sve testove kako biste završili ovaj laboratorijski rad.</p>\n<p><strong>Priče korisnika:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Trebalo bi da kreiraš funkciju nazvanu <code>convertCtoF</code>.</li>\n<li><code>convertCtoF</code> treba da primi jedan numerički argument, koji je temperatura u Celzijusima.</li>\n<li><code>convertCtoF</code> treba da vrati broj.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244b3","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":26,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"introduction-functions-in-javascript","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/introduction-functions-in-javascript/lab-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter/build-a-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da kreirate funkciju nazvanu <code>convertCtoF</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(convertCtoF);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF</code> Treba mu/Trebalo bi da prihvati jedan parametar.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(convertCtoF, 1);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF(0)</code> Trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert.isNumber(convertCtoF(0));"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF(-30)</code> treba da vrati vrednost od <code>-22</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(convertCtoF(-30), -22);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF(-10)</code> treba da vrati vrednost za <code>14</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(convertCtoF(-10), 14);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF(0)</code> treba da vrati vrednost <code>32</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(convertCtoF(0), 32);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF(20)</code> treba da vrati vrednost od <code>68</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(convertCtoF(20), 68);"},{"text":"<p><code>convertCtoF(30)</code> treba da vrati vrednost od <code>86</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(convertCtoF(30), 86);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-functions-in-javascript/#lab-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter","dashedName":"build-a-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter","certification":"introduction-functions-in-javascript","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"introduction-functions-in-javascript","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"lab-celsius-to-fahrenheit-converter","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-functions-in-javascript/lab-counting-cards/lab-counting-cards","prevChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-functions-in-javascript/workshop-loan-qualification-checker/step-7","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244b3","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":26,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function convertCtoF(celsius) {\r\n  let fahrenheit = celsius * (9 / 5) + 32;\r\n  return fahrenheit;\r\n}\r\n\r\nconvertCtoF(30);","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/introduction-functions-in-java